---
title: Katsu Beef & Veggie Egg Noodles with Crushed Peanuts
description: You’ll be off to visit your happy place when you get a taste of this dish. beef mince is tossed in katsu paste and mellowed out with coconut milk to create a perfectly balanced dish, with egg noodles to help slurp up all that sauce!
